tomorrow.

199
00:11:40,974 --> 00:11:42,453
I'll lie on the bed

200
00:11:42,573 --> 00:11:43,533
during the technique class.

201
00:11:44,174 --> 00:11:48,854
Tou Tou, apply pressure
onto his temple exterior.

202
00:11:49,854 --> 00:11:51,294
